## Task 5 — Dark/Light Theme Verification on Mobile

All new mobile components (FilterDrawer, sticky Deal Desk bar, mobile back nav) must
work correctly in both dark and light themes. Specifically:
- FilterDrawer backdrop overlay: `bg-black/50` works in both themes
- FilterDrawer panel: must use `bg-background` (CSS variable), not hardcoded white/black
- Sticky bar: `bg-background border-border` (CSS variables)
- All text: `text-foreground` / `text-muted-foreground` (CSS variables)

Do NOT use hardcoded `bg-white`, `bg-gray-900`, `text-black`, or `text-white` anywhere
in new mobile components.

